    "body": "@jeluard @rachelhamlin sorry for the confusion here\r\n\r\nThere is the same bug when scanning QR code from any of:\r\n`Profile` -> `Extentions` -> tap `Scan QR code` -> scan valid QR code\r\n`Profile` -> `Bootnodes` ->`+` ->  tap `Scan QR code` -> scan valid QR code\r\n`Profile` -> `Mailserver` ->`+` ->  tap `Scan QR code` -> scan valid QR code\r\n\r\nAnd once QR code value read, - there is a redirect to an unexpected screen happens. \r\n\r\nLet me create separate issue for bootnode + mailserver parts as they have higher priority than when scanning QR code part from Extentions view (according to https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/7995#issuecomment-486702002)\r\n",
